Name: Dot Debugger

Use debugging tools to destroy them. Defeat the bugs, save the computer, save the Earth. + 12 Levels + 10 Enemy Types + 2 Bosses + Binary Camouflage System + Freeware + Small Download (18 MB) + Controller Support
